{"id": "1498969638858653838", "channel_id": "1498149263149109399", "author_id": "938065779096702976", "author_name": "charlihohoho", "content": "i stumbled onto this thread and this may be rather late but i also do have a solution that doesnt involve creating a new account - \nyou just need to go to the app store, click on your avatar on the top right, click on your account name (topmost item), (you may have to sign in here), then click on \"Country/Region\" and choose a different region (e.g. HK) which will prompt you to continue to inputting optional payment method and mandatory address + phone number + name (you can make up one tbh since even the number doesnt require verification) and voila you should be able to download morimens global ver. \ndo note that if you have existing subscriptions to apple services e.g. apple music, or existing money in your apple account, or preordered apps, you may have to cancel those services/preorders and finish using your funds before you can switch regions\nhope this helps!", "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:50:11.413000+00:00", "type": 19, "thread_id": "1498149263149109399", "mentions": ["341504770579628032"], "reply_to": "1498579836837433465"}
